snippet.title: AQUAMAN - Final HD Trailer | Jason Momoa ,Amber Heard
snippet.description:
From Warner Bros. Pictures and director James Wan comes an action packed adventure that spans the vast, visually breathtaking underwater world of the seven seas AQUAMAN, starring Jason Momoa in the title role,the film reveals the origin story of half-human, half-atlantean Arthur curry and takes him on the journey of his lifetime one that will not force him to face who he really is, but to discover if he is worthy of who he was born to be, a King


THANK YOU for watching, PLEASE share and subscribe, you are an awesome human being.
